snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play with Musical Instruments for Kids
snippet.description:
Diana plays the drum from the kitchen pan. Dad gives a little girl toy musical instruments. Diana plays drums, guitar, piano and singing. But such toys are too loud! Dad finds a quiet toy for his daughter!
